<br>
Sartha Anne Rose... a name cloaked in mystery and secrets. Only shreds of her past was known to anyone, and the pieces made knowledge held their own secrets. She stood 5'6&quot; with waist-length golden-brown hair and silvery-golden eyes that gleamed with an eternal purpose. She was a proud Amazon, immortal, age unknown. She had been around Themiscrya since close to the beginning, occasionally off on her own adventures when an unwanted past threatened to catch up. She worked mainly alone though her bond with Dawn made them as close as athelfi could get. Sartha would fight alongside her Amazonian Athelfi anytime, but it was only Dawn and a few select people that Sartha truly worked beside. They were the ones she trusted her life with, and they knew who they were.<br>
